| notes          = Demons are the servants of evil. More or less devoted servants of [[Zathroth]], they cause strife and havoc wherever they appear. Their masters are known as [[Demonlord]]s, [[Demon Overlords]] and [[Archdemons]].

They shout {{Sound|CHAMEK ATH UTHUL ARAK!}}, which means "SACRIFICE YOUR BLOOD!", according to [[The Spectres Were Everywhere (Book)|this book]].

You can use a [[Blessed Wooden Stake]] on a slain Demon for a chance to gather some [[Demon Dust]] (see: [[Demon Dust/Dusting]]).
